                <td bgcolor="#000000" valign="top"><font color="#FFFFFF" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;04/28/2003&nbsp;: 1:15:21 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> I just spent 48 to 51 here.  At 49 I was receiving slightly in excess of 1% per kill.  At 50 it dropped to slightly less than 1% per kill.  I set up camp just East of the Southeast corner of the Graveyard.  I used Dooming Darkness, Asystole, BoD, and Panic the Dead and Lich.  At 51 I was getting a yellow bubble of XP every 45 min to an hour.<br /><br />Just sic pet, cast dooming darkness, panic the dead, Asystole/Bond of death, and erfear an decessary.  I never had to leave lich form.<br /><br />Never go into the Graveyard, just pull from the edge.</span></font></td>
