                <td bgcolor="#000000" valign="top"
 nowrap><b><font color="#FFFFFF" face="arial" size="2">smokum</font></b></td>
                <td bgcolor="#000000" valign="top"><font color="#FFFFFF" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;04/07/2003&nbsp;: 5:06:11 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> Was able to pull this off at 44. I got spoiled on those **** droods in WC though, So I would say the fear pathing sucks. Kinda a pain to chase down the corpses to loot. I am much happier watching a mob run back and forth in front of me and being able to loot without standing up! Have not had a single add since I got there, But after the first few go down you again gotta get up and move to be in range to cast. God I am lazy! and where is this little hill you people keep talking about? there isn't 4 square inches of flat ground in that entire zone, there are little hills all over the place!<br /><br />Exp is great. mobs are easy, I am betting this can be done for massive exp even earlier than 44 since all of them have been drk blue to me and I have little or no trouble with resists.<br /><br /><br />Happy Hunting to ya!<br />Smokum (Bowls)<br />Sirname Stripped<br /><br /></span></font></td>
